snippet.title: Empty Shell - Official Accolades Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Watch the latest Empty Shell trailer to see gameplay and what some are saying about this roguelite survival horror game featuring a top-down perspective. Empty Shell is available now on Xbox Series X/S, PS4 (PlayStation 4), PS5 (PlayStation 5), PC and Nintendo Switch.
